videos.description: LSU QB Danny Etling finds WR Stephen Sullivan who runs it in for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Etling hits Sullivan on a post for 43-yard TD

videos.description: Ed Orgeron considering putting in freshman Myles Brennan for spark in second half.
videos.headline: LSU's head coach says there may be a QB change in second half

videos.description: QB Danny Etling goes long to WR Drake Davis for 87-yard touchdown on first play of second half.
videos.headline: Etling opens second half with a rocket pass

videos.description: WR Devin C. Butler took the reverse handoff and threw a strike to WR Ervin Philips on the gadget play.
videos.headline: Syracuse scores first TD on trick play

videos.description: LSU RB Darrel Williams uses a punishing run to score from 20-yards out.
videos.headline: Williams powers his way for TD

videos.description: LSU RB Darrel Williams was wrapped up in the backfield for a Syracuse safety.
videos.headline: Syracuse makes the tackle in the end zone for a safety

videos.description: Syracuse QB Eric Dungey calls his own number and finishes the run for the 14-yard score.
videos.headline: QB Dungey runs it in for the tough TD

videos.description: LSU QB Myles Brennan throws it right to DB Juwan Dowels for LSU's first turnover.
videos.headline: QB Brennan intercepted by DB Dowels as the Tigers were driving

videos.description: QB Eric Dungey does his best Tim Tebow impression and Ravian Pierce brings it down with one hand.
videos.headline: Dungey jump passes to teammate who snags it with one hand

videos.description: WR Steve Ishmael lays out for the touchdown grab, and the Orange are within a score.
videos.headline: Dungey finds Ishmael for TD, puts Syracuse down 2

videos.description: WR D.J. Chark takes the sweep 20 yards for a touchdown to ice the game.
videos.headline: Chark seals the game for LSU with a TD run

videos.description: The LSU coach says Danny Etling talks about how his team escaped.
videos.headline: Coach Ed Orgeron discusses his quarterback situation moving forward

videos.description: QB Danny Etling talks the last touchdown and how QB Myles Brennan played.
videos.headline: Etling talks about the QB rotation

videos.description: The Orange fought hard but it was not enough to beat LSU, even without Derrius Guice.
videos.headline: LSU used a late touchdown to escape against Syracuse

videos.description: Derrius Guice has a quiet day, but the No. 25 Tigers hold off the Orange 35-26.
videos.headline: LSU rebounds from loss to beat Syracuse
